Link to drive image for Raspberry Pi 3.
If you have a lot of devices, it's better to run this image off an external USB hard drive or SSD rather than
a microSD card to avoid wearing out the drive media.

The image is a Raspbian Jessie image, with default login "pi", and password "raspbian".

https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B4OlaiyiwIKtS0tBdDNZaS1ZSzA

